      <body>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-1">
            <heading>Citation, commencement and extent</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-1-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Conservation (Natural Habitats, &amp;c.) Amendment (Scotland) Regulations 2019 and come into force on 1 May 2019.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-1-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>These Regulations extend to Scotland only.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-2">
            <heading>Amendment of the Conservation (Natural Habitats, &amp;c.) Regulations 1994</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <intro>
               <p>Schedule 2 (European protected species of animals) of the Conservation (Natural Habitats, &amp;c.) Regulations 1994<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/> is amended as follows—</p>
            </intro>
            <subparagraph eId="regulation-2-a">
               <num>(a)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>in the first column (common name) of the table, immediately below “Bats, Typical (all species)”, insert “Beaver, Eurasian or European”, and</p>
               </content>
            </subparagraph>
            <subparagraph eId="regulation-2-b">
               <num>(b)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>in the second column (scientific name) of the table, immediately below “Vespertilionidae”, insert “Castor fiber”.</p>
               </content>
            </subparagraph>
         </hcontainer>
